---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const lang = "en";
---

<BaseLayout
  lang={lang}
  title="About Us – Le Ballon Rouge"
  description="Learn about Le Ballon Rouge's mission, vision, values, partnerships and what parents say about our French-language daycare in Hamilton and Brantford."
>

  <!-- Page intro -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pb-10 pt-8 md:pt-12">
    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center">
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-black tracking-tight md:text-5xl">About Us</h1>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-prose text-base font-medium leading-7 text-slate-600 md:text-lg">
          Le Ballon Rouge is a French-language daycare focused on learning through play,
          nurturing routines and a warm environment where every child can thrive.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">
          <a href="#vmv" class="rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white/60 px-3 py-2 hover:bg-white">
            Vision, Mission, Values
          </a>
          <a href="#partenariats" class="rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white/60 px-3 py-2 hover:bg-white">
            Partnerships
          </a>
          <a href="#temoignages" class="rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white/60 px-3 py-2 hover:bg-white">
            Testimonials
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VMV -->
  <section id="vmv" class="scroll-mt-28 mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pb-12">
    <div class="flex items-end justify-between gap-4">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight md:text-3xl">Vision, Mission, Values</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 max-w-2xl text-slate-600 md:text-lg">
          A clear, human and consistent framework to guide our everyday decisions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-7 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-3">
      <article class="rounded-[28px] border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/5 md:p-7">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-slate-900">Vision</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
          To offer a quality French-language environment focused on exploration, curiosity and the joy of learning,
          so every child can progress at their own pace.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-[28px] border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/5 md:p-7">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-slate-900">Mission</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
          To provide a French-language childcare service that supports the overall development of each child,
          in collaboration with families and the community.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-[28px] border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/5 md:p-7">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-slate-900">Values</h3>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 font-bold text-slate-700">
          <li>Kindness and respect.</li>
          <li>Safety and reassuring routines.</li>
          <li>Inclusion and diversity.</li>
          <li>Partnership with parents.</li>
          <li>Excellence and continuous improvement.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 rounded-[28px] border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/5 md:p-8">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-black tracking-tight md:text-2xl">Our story</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
        Le Ballon Rouge evolves with the needs of children and families. We continuously improve our spaces,
        activities and communication tools to offer a consistent, reassuring and stimulating experience.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
        Our goal is simple: create a French-language environment where children learn through play, build confidence,
        and feel welcomed every single day.
      </p>
    </div>

    <a
      href="/en/inscription/"
      class="mt-6 inline-flex w-full justify-center rounded-full bg-red-700 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold text-white shadow-lg shadow-red-700/20 hover:bg-red-800 md:hidden"
    >
      Request a spot
    </a>
  </section>

  <!-- Partnerships -->
  <section id="partenariats" class="scroll-mt-28 mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pb-12">
    <div class="rounded-[28px] border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/5 md:p-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight md:text-3xl">Partnerships</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 max-w-2xl text-slate-600 md:text-lg">
            A network of community and institutional partners who support our families.
          </p>
        </div>

        <a
          href="/en/contact/"
          class="inline-flex rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-extrabold shadow-sm hover:bg-white/80"
        >
          Contact us
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">
        <span class="rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white/60 px-3 py-2">City of Hamilton</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white/60 px-3 py-2">City of Brantford</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white/60 px-3 py-2">EarlyON</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white/60 px-3 py-2">Collège Boréal</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white/60 px-3 py-2">French-language schools</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white/60 px-3 py-2">Local organizations</span>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-6 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2">
        <article class="rounded-3xl border border-black/10 bg-white/60 p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-slate-900">Why these partnerships?</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
            They help us better guide families, enrich our activities and strengthen the local Francophone community.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="rounded-3xl border border-black/10 bg-white/60 p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-slate-900">What does that look like?</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
            Workshops, parent resources, special events and connections with support services.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials -->
  <section id="temoignages" class="scroll-mt-28 mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pb-12">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight md:text-3xl">Testimonials</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 max-w-2xl text-slate-600 md:text-lg">
          A few words from parents about their experience at Le Ballon Rouge.
        </p>
      </div>

      <a
        href="/en/inscription/"
        class="hidden rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-extrabold shadow-sm hover:bg-white/80 md:inline-flex"
      >
        Register
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-7 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      <article class="rounded-[28px] border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/5 md:p-7">
        <div class="inline-flex rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-slate-600">
          Hamilton
        </div>
        <p class="mt-5 text-[1.05rem] font-semibold leading-8 text-slate-800 md:text-lg">
          "An attentive team and clear communication. Our child feels confident and is making great progress."
        </p>
        <p class="mt-5 font-black text-slate-900">Parent</p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-[28px] border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/5 md:p-7">
        <div class="inline-flex rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-slate-600">
          Brantford
        </div>
        <p class="mt-5 text-[1.05rem] font-semibold leading-8 text-slate-800 md:text-lg">
          "We love the French atmosphere and the activities. The routines are reassuring and well structured."
        </p>
        <p class="mt-5 font-black text-slate-900">Parent</p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-[28px] border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/5 md:p-7">
        <div class="inline-flex rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-slate-600">
          Ontario
        </div>
        <p class="mt-5 text-[1.05rem] font-semibold leading-8 text-slate-800 md:text-lg">
          "A very warm welcome from the start. You can feel a real team spirit and an environment truly designed for children."
        </p>
        <p class="mt-5 font-black text-slate-900">Parent</p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 rounded-[28px] border border-black/10 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-50 to-orange-50 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/5 md:p-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between">
        <div class="max-w-2xl">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black tracking-tight md:text-2xl">Want to meet us?</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 leading-7 text-slate-600">
            Request a spot or contact us to learn more about our centres and our approach.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a
            href="/en/inscription/"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-red-700 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold text-white shadow-lg shadow-red-700/20 hover:bg-red-800"
          >
            Request a spot
          </a>
          <a
            href="/en/centres/"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white/80 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-800 shadow-sm hover:bg-white"
          >
            See our centres
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a
      href="/en/inscription/"
      class="mt-6 inline-flex w-full justify-center rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold shadow-sm hover:bg-white/80 md:hidden"
    >
      Register
    </a>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>